{"tid":1093782,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人戒極都戒唔到煙","createTime":"2019-04-05T21:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T02:49:53.000Z","uid":47485,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1862231216d15a94ad76394a08d6385bf0f40eb8","tid":1093782,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:04:15.000Z","msg":"我好記得細個咳過一輪<br />\n氣管不嬲唔好<br />\n但讀書時學左食煙<br />\n自此由16歲開始到依家34歲都戒唔到<br />\n<br />\n其實就30歲果時同自己講<br />\n不如送份生日禮物比自己30歲戒煙<br />\n但30，31，32，33 一直得個想字<br />\n近呢年幾轉食iqos 但氣管仍然係咁咳<br />\n依家心諗 如果再戒唔到<br />\n應該一世都戒唔到<br />\n<br />\n依家有兩條iqos 係屋企唔敢折<br />\n<br />\n依家day 2<br />\n有無過來人分享下心得"},{"pid":"24e65e56cfde32d754151c2899785c56068aba32","tid":1093782,"uid":79349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:06:09.000Z","msg":"飲水"},{"pid":"f0fc8fdc9c0cfb7f2497955e217be041012aa0b7","tid":1093782,"uid":132047,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:08:45.000Z","msg":"食左12年煙已戒8年，以前3日2包醇萬。試下買戒煙貼，好有用。當真係頂唔住時大量飲水然後落街跑步，跑到嘔咁濟應該唔會想食"},{"pid":"aff9d2618db11536f29dd421a6251f424112b625","tid":1093782,"uid":90820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:12:46.000Z","msg":"識人咬香口膠捱過咗嗰個心癮口痕嘅階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打加油呀<br />\n戒煙對健康有好處嘅<br />\n希望你會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a4fa76f66bd8c672b52fa4cda189b9f21a7655","tid":1093782,"uid":169261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:16:50.000Z","msg":"你食開iqos咁我唔知你有無食過vapor，但我就係靠食vapor戒，記住唔好加尼古丁落去，可以滿足手癮同口癮，但又可以幫你減少對尼古丁依賴，可以試下，但講到尾都係毅力問題，無毅力就算有幾好嘅輔助都係無用"},{"pid":"27a7aff89866d08db2c006f5ec51a63db2f44b7e","tid":1093782,"uid":128472,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"續啲續啲戒，唔好逼自己太緊"},{"pid":"92c852b7babc7c490f613a20e4b175343d030187","tid":1093782,"uid":192281,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:19:18.000Z","msg":"先減後戒"},{"pid":"3b95c3b57b9e6a197b5cef3f22cde8bfef0419b0","tid":1093782,"uid":120814,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:19:48.000Z","msg":"咁大個人少少意志力都無, 唔洗戒啦, 太長命都無用"},{"pid":"74ec324a1546222dcd69b73fea88171fb1b67dcb","tid":1093782,"uid":147603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"92c852b7babc7c490f613a20e4b175343d030187","tid":1093782,"uid":192281,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:19:18.000Z","msg":"先減後戒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:38:11.000Z","msg":"都係啲戒唔到煙嘅藉口<br />\n咩由8轉食5結果只係吸得更加入肺<br />\n用替代品仲無咁傷身"},{"pid":"c3cf74c5319bc68c18866a068be1135cf0ea4415","tid":1093782,"uid":116917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T22:04:45.000Z","msg":"中二開始食左十幾年，quit左幾年<br />\n當時咁岩大病，無咩點食，心諗不如索性戒左佢<br />\n<br />\n我迫自己去討厭煙味，覺得煙味好撚臭<br />\n同身邊所有人講我決定戒煙(同自己唔柒得, 無得回頭)<br />\n癮起食珍寶珠<br />\n<br />\n就係呢幾樣野幫左我，希望都幫到你"},{"pid":"e9fd2664611813b3f66ed9b37c0d8fdf137cef61","tid":1093782,"uid":7580,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"以前返過份工成日都要捱通頂無得訓 <br />\n工時又長 2-3日無訓過覺都試過<br />\n嗰時最勁試過1日2-3包 而家諗返起真係好癲<br />\n轉咗返正常office工之後<br />\n慢慢變咗1日4-5支 由8mg 降到4mg 到而家mg1 嘅煙<br />\n之前失業 成個月喺屋企 成個星期唔落街食都得<br />\n所以試吓慢慢降底 加逐啲逐啲咁減少支數 應該會易戒啲"},{"pid":"b8265a45db98d173ed78f7701787b8efed4de6ca","tid":1093782,"uid":25969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T00:47:15.000Z","msg":"戒必適，醫生處方三個月。<br />\n精神科藥物，冇可能戒唔到"},{"pid":"aa4f3296bb014f43adbb9abbc8cfbc5ae033a4cf","tid":1093782,"uid":40039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T01:10:53.000Z","msg":"食電子煙戒左真煙"},{"pid":"d3430b51e2c1fee9c356b8261f66f54bec08fc86","tid":1093782,"uid":190264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"過來人<br />\n我用跑步戒煙既<br />\n我果時頭三日無時無刻都想去食煙<br />\n個身體好似唔食唔得咁<br />\n定時定刻就會響警號嗌你入廁所食煙<br />\n但只要捱過呢個時期 <br />\n一到第4日 你即刻會發現<br />\n你已經唔需要煙了～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29e1d88da3526b2f9a03fbd2b0aebb70851e0f8","tid":1093782,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:32:00.000Z","msg":"21歲仔 已經1日1包左一年幾了"},{"pid":"9eb7a9f224f756da25e514e72a20608d9dbb6639","tid":1093782,"uid":235517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:39:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forms.gle/RrQoxEVca8uDXE9Y7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FRrQoxEVca8uDXE9Y7&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBIw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=2b47ad73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/RrQoxEVca8uDXE9Y7</a><br />\n各位戒煙/食緊煙嘅ching可唔可以幫手填下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e16791f2b195bc03f91170e7a140a59607b9793","tid":1093782,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0fc8fdc9c0cfb7f2497955e217be041012aa0b7","tid":1093782,"uid":132047,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:08:45.000Z","msg":"食左12年煙已戒8年，以前3日2包醇萬。試下買戒煙貼，好有用。當真係頂唔住時大量飲水然後落街跑步，跑到嘔咁濟應該唔會想食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"你咁長煙齡<br />\n理論上都難戒<br />\n<br />\n我今日day 3 試下落街跑下"},{"pid":"a90a4980140f0d59dea75d77a25fdd7014e75f8b","tid":1093782,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24e65e56cfde32d754151c2899785c56068aba32","tid":1093782,"uid":79349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:06:09.000Z","msg":"飲水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"飲多d水係舒服d<br />\n但個人不其然會諗起食煙"},{"pid":"d63de49af5fba5c4a0e66ec661ec871417da1f84","tid":1093782,"uid":47485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9a4fa76f66bd8c672b52fa4cda189b9f21a7655","tid":1093782,"uid":169261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:16:50.000Z","msg":"你食開iqos咁我唔知你有無食過vapor，但我就係靠食vapor戒，記住唔好加尼古丁落去，可以滿足手癮同口癮，但又可以幫你減少對尼古丁依賴，可以試下，但講到尾都係毅力問題，無毅力就算有幾好嘅輔助都係無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"Vapor 好似都幾好喎<br />\n不過癈事又特登買d設備喇<br />\n不過用意志力控制唔食煙<br />\n個心會好癢"},{"pid":"5ad85828fb6b102075b9cdef7c4d5d1da03244a0","tid":1093782,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"飲多 d 水，食多 d 生果，可以幫助排返 d 毒出嚟，中醫係咁講嘅<br />\n<br />\n我個時戒煙會夜晚訓唔到，醫生開咗 d 黃丸仔俾我(收鼻水抗敏感藥，食完超眼訓)<br />\n仲勁爆暗瘡同飛滋，睇中醫飲幾劑茶幫助排毒<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係，無論如何都唔好俾藉口自己再食返"},{"pid":"6d69e22a5de4eeca492c1425519a9c8466d3a3d5","tid":1093782,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"本身食左6年<br />\n上年11月去照肺照到有影<br />\n嚇死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後照多2次，醫生話無事<br />\n然後我就立即戒<br />\n一次就成功左到而家都差唔多半年無食過<br />\n<br />\n我有幾個心得<br />\n掉左包煙同火機<br />\n遠離食煙既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同d朋友講你開始戒，比佢地鼓勵下就會好有動力堅持落去<br />\n同埋減少平時出街等人既時間<br />\n做下其他野分下心咁<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f136b64e153d594441568375839292e1fc49790a","tid":1093782,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"出左黎做野後先食 <br />\n有時想唔食就唔食 可幾個星期都唔食 <br />\n但記得第一次食係因為個人亂個心又迷茫 同個老友一人一支第一次就一晚隊哂成包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05562d8bfd9db984cfcfb48dd328f24cdb78a02","tid":1093782,"uid":18553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"食到食吾刀米吾食lor= ="},{"pid":"d6af591be902703c417740f67c579ce421067e71","tid":1093782,"uid":247154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"死咪戒到"},{"pid":"32edf0d060af732d9a1835b809126e6cb2767da5","tid":1093782,"uid":125999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T01:21:54.000Z","msg":"食左15年, 以前一日半包左右, 早幾年開始扁桃腺不停出事, <br />\n又發炎又高燒又痛到食都食唔到訓又訓唔到, 出事呢段期間煙都無心機食, 好返之後已經無再食過煙. 宜家連心癮都無埋."}]}